{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, however, general-purpose LLMs differ in their policies regarding the generation of medical or mental health advice.",
    "Bard's accuracy ratings were impacted by Bard's policy to advise consulting a health care provider when asked questions about mental health.",
    "This practice protects individuals from potential harm, though such responses received lower ratings of quality in this study.LLM-generated answers to mental health questions may not be comparable to human-generated answers, however.",
    "It is critical for LLMs to meet or exceed human performance in order for LLMs to be trusted and to ease the demand for human providers.",
    "In the case of Psy-LLM and ChatGPT, there is evidence that responses to mental health and substance use questions fall short of human-generated responses in dimensions such as accuracy, quality, and alignment with evidence-based practice (EBP) [10,12].Another way that LLMs may serve to educate is to support provider training."
  ]
}